{"content":"From d6576a0af3973c2bce253bbf2b5bc6d9581c1803 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001\nFrom: randymcmillan <randy.lee.mcmillan@gmail.com>\nDate: Fri, 15 Sep 2023 11:07:04 -0400\nSubject: [PATCH] gnostr.org:nevent1qqstxe9972fwq0pphc0uq2cgn7u2lqr3udm4sg7z4ae29pr5h2tzaycpz3mhxue69uhhyetvv9ujuerpd46hxtnfdu4jpvuc\n\n---\n .gitignore                                                                                              |  1 +\n CNAME                                                                                                   |  1 +\n README.md                                                                                               |  9 +++++++++\n clone                                                                                                   | 17 +++++++++++++++++\n icon.svg                                                                                                | 66 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n index.html                                                                                              | 10 ++++++++++\n nevent1qqstxe9972fwq0pphc0uq2cgn7u2lqr3udm4sg7z4ae29pr5h2tzaycpz3mhxue69uhhyetvv9ujuerpd46hxtnfdu4jpvuc |  0\n 7 files changed, 104 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 .gitignore\n create mode 100644 CNAME\n create mode 100755 README.md\n create mode 100755 clone\n create mode 100644 icon.svg\n create mode 100644 index.html\n create mode 100644 nevent1qqstxe9972fwq0pphc0uq2cgn7u2lqr3udm4sg7z4ae29pr5h2tzaycpz3mhxue69uhhyetvv9ujuerpd46hxtnfdu4jpvuc\n\ndiff --git a/.gitignore b/.gitignore\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 0000000..d0a3534\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/.gitignore\n@@ -0,0 +1 @@\n+.gnostr\ndiff --git a/CNAME b/CNAME\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 0000000..b0da186\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/CNAME\n@@ -0,0 +1 @@\n+github.gnostr.org\ndiff --git a/README.md b/README.md\nnew file mode 100755\nindex 0000000..f04079a\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/README.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+# gnostr.org\n+\n+##### a git+nostr version control system\n+\n+<html><center>\n+\n+![](icon.svg)\n+\n+</center></html>\ndiff --git a/clone b/clone\nnew file mode 100755\nindex 0000000..a22a466\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/clone\n@@ -0,0 +1,17 @@\n+#!/usr/bin/env bash\n+\n+gh repo list gnostr-org --limit 1000 | while read -r repo _; do\n+  RESULT=\"${repo//gnostr-org/public}\"\n+  echo \"cloning $repo into $RESULT\"\n+  gh repo clone \"$repo\" \"$RESULT\" -- -q 2>/dev/null || (\n+    echo \"updating $RESULT\"\n+    cd \"$RESULT\"\n+    # Handle case where local checkout is on a non-main/master branch\n+    # - ignore checkout errors because some repos may have zero commits,\n+    # so no main or master\n+    git checkout -q main   2>/dev/null || true\n+    git checkout -q master 2>/dev/null || true\n+    git checkout -q readme 2>/dev/null || true\n+    git pull -q\n+  )\n+done\ndiff --git a/icon.svg b/icon.svg\nnew file mode 100644\nindex 0000000..c20d6bc\n--- /dev/null\n+++ b/icon.svg\n@@ -0,0 +1,66 @@\n+\n+<svg\n+  version=\"1.1\"\n+  baseProfile=\"full\"\n+  xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\n+  xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"\n+  viewbox=\"0 0 666 666\"\n+  width=\"666\"\n+  height=\"666\"\n+>\n+<style>\n+#outline {\n+  stroke: #111;\n+  stroke-width: 101.73790276344452;\n+  fill: none;\n+}\n+.dot {\n+  fill: #111;\n+}\n+.point {\n+  fill: #111;\n+}\n+/*.point:nth-child(odd) {\n+  fill: rgb(165, 24, 201);\n+}*/\n+.ray {\n+  stroke: #111;\n+  stroke-width: 101.73790276344452;\n+}\n+/*.ray:nth-child(even) {\n+  stroke: rgb(165, 24, 201);\n+}*/\n+#background {\n+  fill: #FCFCFC;\n+  stroke: none;\n+}\n+#pupil {\n+  fill: rgb(165, 24, 201);\n+}\n+</style>\n+<!-- <g transform=\"translate(333, 333)\">\n+     <circle id=\"background\" r=\"1070.000000\"/>\n+     <circle id=\"outline\" r=\"529.037094\"/>\n+     <circle id=\"pupil\" r=\"82.307692\"/> -->\n+<!-- \t<line class=\"ray\" x1=\"803.646713\" y1=\"0.000000\" x2=\"164.615385\" y2=\"0.000000\" />\n+\t<line class=\"ray\" x1=\"568.264040\" y1=\"568.264